  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to characterize the safety and efficacy profile of ACP-196
      (acalabrutinib) in subjects with relapsed or refractory Mantle Cell Lymphoma (MCL).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
